<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3153031" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="6"><switchinline select="appl"><caseinline select="WRITER">If you click the<emph> Decrease Indent</emph> icon while holding down the <switchinline select="sys"><caseinline select="MAC">Command key
</caseinline><defaultinline>Ctrl key</defaultinline></switchinline>, the indent for the selected paragraph is moved by the default tab stop that has been set under <link href="text/shared/optionen/01040200.xhp" name="Tools - Options - Writer - General"><emph>Tools - Options - %PRODUCTNAME Writer - General</emph></link> .
</caseinline></switchinline></paragraph>
